{"tid":424512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個fd 跌左個窗落街","createTime":"2017-10-04T18:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T18:43:36.000Z","uid":75660,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7c75bdf7b8bc29486efd69514d10890a9e2a59","tid":424512,"uid":75660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T18:25:11.000Z","msg":"交代少少背景先，我個fd 住果度舊區黎，<br />\n<br />\n附近好多地都開始用作重建用途。<br />\n<br />\n佢間房起碼23年無裝修，<br />\n<br />\n佢成日睇電視笑d 跌窗意外事故，<br />\n<br />\n話無咩可能發生，覺得呢d 事幾可發生。<br />\n<br />\n頭先訓訓吓教，收到佢wtsapp message，<br />\n<br />\n話跌左個窗出街😐，我以為佢講笑（成日吹水），<br />\n<br />\n咁我梗係無理佢訓我既覺。跟住再收到知通知：［真架喂］<br />\n<br />\n我再好耐無裝修過兼且又少打理間房。<br />\n<br />\n頭先佢wtsapp send張相黎，話佢個窗跌引用左落街。<br />\n<br />\n我以為佢講笑無理佢，打開wtsapp，<br />\n<br />\n見到佢Send左張圖黎，咁我下載黎睇啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/05/022104_035a5c744de1ac55827eec8bc3b0c1e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F05%2F022104_035a5c744de1ac55827eec8bc3b0c1e7.jpg&h=46c26c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/05/022104_dc2ecc49fab09ca037c5f21754fc0988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F05%2F022104_dc2ecc49fab09ca037c5f21754fc0988.jpg&h=af32a2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係跌左落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617aff94306a58b7b850280903340e3923e4b59c","tid":424512,"uid":151245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T18:31:05.000Z","msg":"睇咗你個fd喺窗跌落街"},{"pid":"7020aab946e7a07d8608aeea2a0f32d0c3efe6c9","tid":424512,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0